a.n: The Amazing World of Gumball I

p.k: The Laziest / The Ghost / The Mystery / The Prank Gumball and Darwin challenge Dad to a “lazy-off”. / Gumball must learn to say “no” when Carrie the Ghost uses his body against his will. / Gumball sets out to solve the mystery of who stuffed Principal Brown into his locker. / Gumball and Darwin’s harmless pranks on Dad spiral hopelessly out of control.
